reviews.text: Nice little coffee place. Unfortunately no vegan food option and no vegan milk option for cappuccino.
Competiter is more，Customer is less that before. Maybe. This is the environment that a café should have. Air is fresher，Coffee is better，Feel have much more .

Food: My friend had spaghetti carbonara and the flavour is kind of HK style, sadly the portion is too small like an entree. I had egg benedict and the taste is fine, portion is too small for girls.

Drinks: Flat White (okay)+ Hot Peach Tea (bitterness)

 Price:
Very cozy and comfortable environment with awesome barista and fantastic coffee! I personally like the one called "Dirty". Very special texture. Worth trying
Relaxing place, all food and coffee are made with heart

result.name: Cafe Heato

reviews.text:
2019.05.29

魔女@海圖 Cafe Heato

Doudle Espresso $30

咖啡師說偏果酸。
“可以，試一下。”

果酸濃，但不尖銳，
酸後有果香，
Body 有一點點厚。

手沖 $60
魔女
Ethiopia
水洗

一開始擺出來的豆沒什麼特別。
“我喜歡特別的。”
咖啡師從架上取出一袋：魔女。
改名真的很重要，
光這個名就吸引。

“因為你喜歡深烘焙，我把酸做低一點。”

第一口：茶。
“如何？”
“很茶，高質的茶，不是混濁、低價的茶。不過其他味不明顯。”
咖啡師笑笑。
後半段，檸檬味出來，不酸，
盲測的話，會以為是檸檬茶。

店向內街，
櫥窗玻璃寫滿老闆的人生節理，
上次往樂啡時經過看到，覺得蠻特別，就想試。
店內告示不要催單，
只賣咖啡相關，
不賣茶餐廳東西，
有性格的店，不會太差。

屯門新墟青柏徑6號鹿苑16號舖

#屯門咖啡店
#香港

一間喜歡的cafe, 除all day breakfast 外，也有意粉!
食物質素一般 ，但價錢貴。 環境舒適度尚可，但 員工服務態度差， 基本禮貌欠奉 冇下次

reviews.text: Chilled out place. It's a bit expensive but it's nice, quiet and clean.

Nice local coffee place with some food and some cakes on the menu. The coffee here is nice and you could have moat kind of different coffees. Can be a bit crowded but it is quite spacious on the inside.
nice place~
Relaxing place with good food and service

This cafe is very cosy.  This place is very suitable for leisure and time killing .  Maybe this cafe is in an alley, only a few customers was in the cafe.  Like other cafe, potable water and Wifi are complimentary.  The only minor problem is that the odour of food was a bit strong when cooking, due to its design of an open kitchen.

reviews.text: 好hea的咖啡室😁
特色小店, 由店內的佈置睇得出店主用心的安排, 有酒類飲品, 食物質素唔錯, 叫了一個意大利粉（$75), Ice drip($45) Nut味重, 尾段回甘(但……落冰?!). 屯門區來講價錢在中上位.
員工服務好，環境舒適。  價錢合理
